    "description": "Expanded-body line on the GPS diagnostics card (#1458 phase 2.5 / #2765) reporting the single largest interval observed between two GPS fixes, in whole seconds — the worst-case throttling moment of the trip.",
    "placeholders": {
      "seconds": {
        "type": "int"
      }
    }
